Laurie Matthews (Laurence Charles Matthews, born 1956) founded Caretakers Cottage a youth homelessness service in Sydney, Australia and currently serves as CEO. Laurie was also a founding member Yfoundations, a peak body organisation for youth homelessness in New South Wales. and has served on the Yfoundations board for a number of years between 1989 and 2011.
Laurie also serves on the board of Southern Youth and Family Services, a homelessness service based in Wollongong, New South Wales.
